snippet.title: Dragon Quest IV (NES) - Japanese TV Commercial
snippet.description: This is a Japanese TV commercial for Dragon Quest IV.  They seem to have been going for a hipper vibe with this ad campaign compared to that of previous games in the series.  Provided by http://www.iheartdragonquest.com.
